class Solution:
    def maximumValueSum(self, board: List[List[int]]) -> int:
        maxr = [0]*len(board)
        for i in range(len(board)):
            x = board[i]
            t1 = 0
            if x[1] >= x[t1]: t1,t2 = 1,t1
            else: t2 = 1
            if x[2] >= x[t1]: t1,t2,t3 = 2,t1,t2
            elif x[2] >= x[t2]: t2,t3 = 2,t2
            else: t3 = 2
            # print(t1,t2,t3)
            for j in range(3,len(x)):
                if x[j] >= x[t1]: t1,t2,t3 = j,t1,t2
                elif x[j] >= x[t2]: t2,t3 = j,t2
                elif x[j] >= x[t3]: t3 = j
            maxr[i] = (t1,t2,t3)
        # print(maxr)
        ans = board[0][0]+board[1][1]+board[2][2]
        for i in range(len(board)-2):
            for j in range(i+1,len(board)-1):
                for k in range(j+1,len(board)):
                    x = maxr[i][0]
                    y = maxr[j][0] if maxr[j][0] != x else maxr[j][1]
                    z = maxr[k][0] if maxr[k][0] != x and maxr[k][0] != y else (maxr[k][1] if maxr[k][1] != x and maxr[k][1] != y else maxr[k][2])
                    ans = max(ans,board[i][x]+board[j][y]+board[k][z])

                    x = maxr[i][0]
                    z = maxr[k][0] if maxr[k][0] != x else maxr[k][1]
                    y = maxr[j][0] if maxr[j][0] != x and maxr[j][0] != z else (maxr[j][1] if maxr[j][1] != x and maxr[j][1] != z else maxr[j][2])
                    ans = max(ans,board[i][x]+board[j][y]+board[k][z])

                    z = maxr[k][0]
                    x = maxr[i][0] if maxr[i][0] != z else maxr[i][1]
                    y = maxr[j][0] if maxr[j][0] != x and maxr[j][0] != z else (maxr[j][1] if maxr[j][1] != x and maxr[j][1] != z else maxr[j][2])
                    ans = max(ans,board[i][x]+board[j][y]+board[k][z])

                    y = maxr[j][0]
                    x = maxr[i][0] if maxr[i][0] != y else maxr[i][1]
                    z = maxr[k][0] if maxr[k][0] != x and maxr[k][0] != y else (maxr[k][1] if maxr[k][1] != x and maxr[k][1] != y else maxr[k][2])
                    ans = max(ans,board[i][x]+board[j][y]+board[k][z])

                    z = maxr[k][0]
                    y = maxr[j][0] if maxr[j][0] != z else maxr[j][1]
                    x = maxr[i][0] if maxr[i][0] != y and maxr[i][0] != z else (maxr[i][1] if maxr[i][1] != y and maxr[i][1] != z else maxr[i][2])
                    ans = max(ans,board[i][x]+board[j][y]+board[k][z])

                    y = maxr[j][0]
                    z = maxr[k][0] if maxr[k][0] != y else maxr[k][1]
                    x = maxr[i][0] if maxr[i][0] != y and maxr[i][0] != z else (maxr[i][1] if maxr[i][1] != y and maxr[i][1] != z else maxr[i][2])
                    ans = max(ans,board[i][x]+board[j][y]+board[k][z])
        return ans
